# LCVB API keys — copy this file to `.env` and fill in real values.
# The pipeline auto-loads `.env` at the repo root via openrouter_client._load_dotenv.
#
# Which keys you need depends on which models you plan to run:
#
#   - ANTHROPIC_API_KEY: required for any Anthropic-routed subject runs
#     (Haiku / Sonnet / Opus) AND for the judge model used to score every
#     subject run (the judge is always Haiku 4.5 for cross-model
#     comparability, regardless of which subject model you ran).
#
#   - OPENROUTER_API_KEY: required for OpenAI, Gemini, Qwen, GPT-OSS,
#     DeepSeek, and other models routed via OpenRouter (any slug
#     containing a `/`).
#
# At minimum you need ANTHROPIC_API_KEY (for the judge). Add
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY if you want to run any subject model that isn't
# Anthropic-native.

ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-your-key-here
